WEBVTT

00:07.041 --> 00:09.000
- Hey...

00:09.041 --> 00:12.667
Hey Mom, Mom...

00:12.709 --> 00:15.417
- What, what?

00:15.458 --> 00:18.041
- I uh, I gotta go to work,

00:18.083 --> 00:19.667
but I'm not feelin' too good.

00:19.709 --> 00:20.959
Is there any orange juice?

00:27.125 --> 00:28.959
- I think we're out.

00:31.250 --> 00:34.291
[ all coughing ]

00:35.834 --> 00:37.500
[ groans ]

00:41.375 --> 00:43.583
- So, we're all sick?

00:43.625 --> 00:46.000
- Well--

00:43.625 --> 00:46.000
- No, I'm fine.

00:46.041 --> 00:47.834
I'm not sick

00:46.041 --> 00:47.834
and I'm going to play

00:47.875 --> 00:49.500
in the Dadminton tournament.

00:49.542 --> 00:51.166
- Wait, what's "Dadminton?"

00:51.208 --> 00:54.291
- It's a badminton tournament,

00:51.208 --> 00:54.291
for Dads only.

00:54.333 --> 00:56.709
So Mom can't play.

00:56.750 --> 00:58.750
- Mom doesn't care!

01:00.583 --> 01:02.375
- Mom, I'm ready.

01:02.417 --> 01:04.125
- Oh baby, c'mon,

01:04.166 --> 01:06.625
you were up sick all night,

01:04.166 --> 01:06.625
you can't go.

01:06.667 --> 01:09.333
- AHHHH!!!!

01:09.375 --> 01:11.125
- Yeah, still can't go.

01:12.542 --> 01:14.709
- Henry, will you

01:12.542 --> 01:14.709
please tell Mom

01:14.750 --> 01:16.542
what a big deal Glozella is?!?

01:16.583 --> 01:18.375
- It's a big deal.

01:18.417 --> 01:20.208
What's Glozella?

01:20.250 --> 01:23.500
- Ugh! It's a huge

01:20.250 --> 01:23.500
music festival,

01:23.542 --> 01:24.917
and it's in Swellview this year,

01:24.959 --> 01:26.500
and Glozella is hosting it,

01:26.542 --> 01:30.208
and I love music and Glozella

01:26.542 --> 01:30.208
so I'm going!!!

01:30.250 --> 01:32.458
- Piper, I'm sorry,

01:32.500 --> 01:35.000
but you are too sick

01:32.500 --> 01:35.000
to go to Glozella.

01:35.041 --> 01:36.458
- Mom!!!

01:36.500 --> 01:39.333
- And you are too sick

01:36.500 --> 01:39.333
to play nerd tennis...

01:39.375 --> 01:40.875
- Wife!!!

01:40.917 --> 01:43.125
- And you are too sick

01:40.917 --> 01:43.125
to go to work.

01:43.166 --> 01:45.083
- Oh come on!

01:45.125 --> 01:47.500
My boss is expecting me

01:45.125 --> 01:47.500
to go do a hard day's work.

01:47.542 --> 01:49.166
And you're sayin'

01:47.542 --> 01:49.166
I should just...

01:49.208 --> 01:51.917
just sit at home and...

01:49.208 --> 01:51.917
and chill and relax?

01:51.959 --> 01:53.375
- Yeah.

01:53.417 --> 01:54.917
- Okay.

01:58.625 --> 02:00.458
I just gotta...

01:58.625 --> 02:00.458
I just gotta call my boss

02:00.500 --> 02:02.000
and--and tell him

02:00.500 --> 02:02.000
I'm not comin' in.

02:05.000 --> 02:07.125
I usually make

02:05.000 --> 02:07.125
my calls outside...

02:08.375 --> 02:11.166
on the porch...

02:11.208 --> 02:12.959
by myself--okay.

02:22.667 --> 02:25.917
Hey Ray...

02:22.667 --> 02:25.917
[ coughing ] Ray...

02:25.959 --> 02:28.375
- Hey, you're supposed

02:25.959 --> 02:28.375
to be getting to work now,

02:28.417 --> 02:29.625
why aren't you here?

02:29.667 --> 02:31.458
- Uh, 'cuz I can't

02:29.667 --> 02:31.458
come in to work--I'm sick.

02:31.500 --> 02:33.417
- Oh, so you're in the hospital?

02:33.458 --> 02:36.000
- Uh... Well, no,

02:33.458 --> 02:36.000
I'm not in the hospital

02:36.041 --> 02:37.333
but I'm not feelin' that--

02:37.375 --> 02:39.375
- Henry, we're crime fighters.

02:39.417 --> 02:41.792
And since criminals don't

02:39.417 --> 02:41.792
blow off work when they're sick,

02:41.834 --> 02:44.500
neither do Captain Man

02:41.834 --> 02:44.500
and Kid Danger. You catchin' my

02:41.834 --> 02:44.500
wave?

02:44.542 --> 02:45.667
- Ray...

02:45.709 --> 02:46.834
- I mean, you ever seen

02:45.709 --> 02:46.834
me blow off work?

02:46.875 --> 02:48.083
- Okay, that's not fair!

02:48.125 --> 02:50.083
- Why is it not fair?

02:48.125 --> 02:50.083
- Because!

02:50.125 --> 02:51.667
You've been indestructible

02:50.125 --> 02:51.667
since you were eight,

02:51.709 --> 02:53.041
you can't get sick!

02:53.083 --> 02:56.125
- That's right, so...

02:53.083 --> 02:56.125
be more like me.

02:57.125 --> 02:59.834
- Look, my mom says I can't

02:57.125 --> 02:59.834
come in to work, so...

02:59.875 --> 03:01.834
- Your mom?

02:59.875 --> 03:01.834
- Yeah.

03:01.875 --> 03:03.250
- Want me to come talk to her?

03:03.291 --> 03:05.458
- Okay, you know what?

03:03.291 --> 03:05.458
I'll be there in ten minutes.

03:05.500 --> 03:06.667
- Nehahahahaha!

03:23.375 --> 03:25.500
- Yeah...

03:25.542 --> 03:28.208
aw yeah...

03:25.542 --> 03:28.208
that's nice...

03:28.250 --> 03:29.834
look at me...

03:34.417 --> 03:37.709
- [ coughing ]

03:34.417 --> 03:37.709
Hey everybody.

03:37.750 --> 03:39.000
- Hi, Henry.

03:37.750 --> 03:39.000
- Hey, Hen.

03:40.750 --> 03:42.208
- [ sneezes ]

03:42.250 --> 03:44.166
- No sneezing.

03:45.417 --> 03:47.250
- Hey, you sick, too?

03:47.291 --> 03:51.166
- Nooo, I'm just collecting

03:47.291 --> 03:51.166
a giant pile of dirty tissues.

03:52.333 --> 03:53.917
- That's gross.

03:57.083 --> 03:58.709
- Hey everybody!

03:58.750 --> 04:00.750
- Hey what's up?

03:58.750 --> 04:00.750
- Hey Schwoz.

04:00.792 --> 04:03.417
- Since it's Saturday morning,

04:03.458 --> 04:06.709
look what I brought!

04:03.458 --> 04:06.709
Cupcakes!

04:06.750 --> 04:10.041
- Oh!

04:06.750 --> 04:10.041
- Sweet.

04:10.083 --> 04:12.709
- Hey Henry,

04:10.083 --> 04:12.709
grab me one would ya?

04:12.750 --> 04:14.583
- Uh, yeah sure.

04:14.625 --> 04:16.125
- Daaaahh!!!

04:19.667 --> 04:21.375
- Dang it, Schwoz!!!

04:21.417 --> 04:23.291
- Aw, the cupcakes...

04:26.750 --> 04:28.125
- Everything's fine.

04:31.500 --> 04:32.959
- What's goin' on with him?

04:33.000 --> 04:35.333
- I dunno.

04:33.000 --> 04:35.333
He's acting kinda'...

04:35.375 --> 04:37.500
[ coughs ]

04:38.500 --> 04:40.291
- Ugggghhh,

04:40.333 --> 04:42.583
am I gonna have to listen

04:40.333 --> 04:42.583
to that all day?

04:44.166 --> 04:45.458
[ blows nose ]

04:47.417 --> 04:50.542
- Uh hey, y'know my

04:47.417 --> 04:50.542
whole family's sick, too?

04:47.417 --> 04:50.542
- No.

04:50.583 --> 04:51.959
Jasper, how you feelin'?

04:52.000 --> 04:53.041
- Great.

04:52.000 --> 04:53.041
Just gettin' a little tired

04:53.083 --> 04:54.250
of holding these paints.

04:54.291 --> 04:55.625
- Higher.

04:57.959 --> 05:00.458
- Hello.

05:00.500 --> 05:02.500
So uh...

05:02.542 --> 05:05.000
did anyone here recently

05:05.041 --> 05:07.291
go into my science laboratory?

05:07.333 --> 05:09.333
- Well, yeah.

05:09.375 --> 05:11.709
- You sent me, Charlotte

05:09.375 --> 05:11.709
and Jasper there on Thursday.

05:11.750 --> 05:14.208
- To put labels on your beakers.

05:14.250 --> 05:16.083
- Okay, well...

05:16.125 --> 05:17.834
I think I did a bad thing.

05:19.166 --> 05:20.792
- What did you do?

05:20.834 --> 05:24.000
- Well, you know how

05:20.834 --> 05:24.000
I've always wanted to be famous?

05:24.041 --> 05:26.500
By curing some terrible disease?

05:26.542 --> 05:28.291
- Yeah.

05:26.542 --> 05:28.291
- Uh-huh.

05:28.333 --> 05:30.792
- So, I figured...

05:30.834 --> 05:32.875
the fastest way

05:30.834 --> 05:32.875
to come up with a cure

05:32.917 --> 05:36.834
was to create my own

05:32.917 --> 05:36.834
terrible disease.

05:36.875 --> 05:38.458
- What?!?

05:36.875 --> 05:38.458
- What?

05:38.500 --> 05:39.959
- Ah...Classic Schwoz.

05:42.166 --> 05:43.625
- Hold on. Hold on.

05:43.667 --> 05:45.875
Are you're saying

05:43.667 --> 05:45.875
that you think

05:45.917 --> 05:47.709
we have that disease

05:45.917 --> 05:47.709
that you created?

05:47.750 --> 05:49.166
- Well...

05:49.208 --> 05:50.583
- He--he doesn't know that!

05:50.625 --> 05:52.750
I mean, maybe we just

05:50.625 --> 05:52.750
have a cold or...

05:52.792 --> 05:55.166
or the flu or...

05:52.792 --> 05:55.166
or dandruff!

05:55.208 --> 05:57.458
- Yeah, Schwoz, you don't

05:55.208 --> 05:57.458
know why they're sick,

05:57.500 --> 05:58.709
you're not a doctor.

05:58.750 --> 06:01.208
- I know what I'm talking about!

06:01.250 --> 06:03.542
Look at Henry's

06:01.250 --> 06:03.542
pinky fingers!

06:03.583 --> 06:05.583
- Oh yeah.

06:03.583 --> 06:05.583
Why are they green?

06:05.625 --> 06:08.333
- It's one of the symptoms

06:05.625 --> 06:08.333
of my disease.

06:08.375 --> 06:10.834
- Ahhhh!!!

06:08.375 --> 06:10.834
My pinkies are green, too!

06:10.875 --> 06:13.375
- Let me see!

06:18.166 --> 06:19.542
[ bell rings ]

06:19.583 --> 06:22.375
- Yah.

06:19.583 --> 06:22.375
You both have my disease.

06:22.417 --> 06:25.542
- Ahhhh great!

06:25.583 --> 06:27.041
- Well, what about Jasper?

06:27.083 --> 06:28.333
He was with us.

06:28.375 --> 06:31.500
He touched your beakers.

06:31.542 --> 06:32.417
Does he have your disease?

06:32.458 --> 06:33.917
- Let me see here...

06:35.500 --> 06:37.583
- [ giggles ]

06:38.917 --> 06:40.500
[ buzzer sounds ]

06:40.542 --> 06:43.875
- Jasper is clean, no disease.

06:43.917 --> 06:46.166
- Well we have it,

06:43.917 --> 06:46.166
why doesn't he?!?

06:46.208 --> 06:48.458
- I-I don't know why

06:46.208 --> 06:48.458
Jasper doesn't have it.

06:48.500 --> 06:52.041
He should.

06:48.500 --> 06:52.041
My disease is very contagious.

06:53.625 --> 06:55.417
- Well, what do

06:53.625 --> 06:55.417
Henry and I do now?!?

06:55.458 --> 06:57.125
- Yeah!

06:55.458 --> 06:57.125
And what about my family?!?

06:57.166 --> 06:58.709
- I can answer that.

06:58.750 --> 07:00.709
Schwoz, you better

06:58.750 --> 07:00.709
come up with a cure

07:00.750 --> 07:02.500
for your stupid disease.

07:00.750 --> 07:02.500
- Okay...

07:02.542 --> 07:05.125
- And until he does...Henry,

07:02.542 --> 07:05.125
since you're both contagious,

07:05.166 --> 07:06.709
you and Charlotte are

07:05.166 --> 07:06.709
gonna have to be quarantined

07:06.750 --> 07:07.959
in your house,

07:06.750 --> 07:07.959
with your family.

07:09.667 --> 07:11.083
- What is quarantined?

07:11.125 --> 07:13.667
- It means that they

07:11.125 --> 07:13.667
all have to stay inside,

07:13.709 --> 07:15.375
so they don't spread the disease

07:15.417 --> 07:17.792
to the normal people

07:15.417 --> 07:17.792
of Swellview.

07:17.834 --> 07:20.291
- Well--well,

07:17.834 --> 07:20.291
what about you?

07:20.333 --> 07:22.667
- Haha!

07:20.333 --> 07:22.667
Don't worry about me.

07:22.709 --> 07:25.834
Old Uncle Ray's indestructible,

07:22.709 --> 07:25.834
which means...

07:25.875 --> 07:28.000
can't get sick.

07:25.875 --> 07:28.000
[ coughs ]

07:29.417 --> 07:30.625
- AHHHHHH!!!

07:30.792 --> 07:32.208
I don't know.

07:33.333 --> 07:34.709
- AHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!!!

07:36.250 --> 07:39.458
Wh-wh-wha...

07:40.709 --> 07:42.333
- It all just kinda happened.

07:42.375 --> 07:43.709
I wanted an after-school job.

07:43.750 --> 07:44.875
But then,

07:43.750 --> 07:44.875
an indestructible superhero

07:44.917 --> 07:46.250
hired me to be his sidekick.

07:46.291 --> 07:47.709
- Ah!

07:47.750 --> 07:48.834
- Now we blow bubbles...

07:48.875 --> 07:50.500
and fight crime.

07:48.875 --> 07:50.500
- Feels good.

07:50.542 --> 07:52.875
[ theme music ]

08:04.834 --> 08:06.166
- Call it.

08:04.834 --> 08:06.166
- Up the tube!

08:08.208 --> 08:10.041
- Aw, my boot!

08:08.208 --> 08:10.041
- Ha!

08:15.875 --> 08:19.000
[ all coughing

08:15.875 --> 08:19.000
and groaning ]

08:22.375 --> 08:25.375
- Oh, will you stop

08:22.375 --> 08:25.375
itchin' and moanin'?

08:26.875 --> 08:28.834
- Yeah, we're just

08:26.875 --> 08:28.834
as sick as you.

08:28.875 --> 08:30.333
- But you don't understand!

08:30.375 --> 08:32.375
My head! Like...

08:32.417 --> 08:33.917
Awww it like...aches!

08:33.959 --> 08:35.542
- Okay,that's called

08:33.959 --> 08:35.542
"a headache."

08:35.583 --> 08:36.917
- Well I don't like it!

08:36.959 --> 08:38.709
Ow!

08:38.750 --> 08:41.291
- Okay.

08:38.750 --> 08:41.291
How's everyone doing?

08:41.333 --> 08:42.917
- How are we doing?

08:42.959 --> 08:44.375
- Look at our fingers.

08:46.500 --> 08:48.000
- D'aaaahh!

08:48.041 --> 08:52.250
Ehhh...

08:48.041 --> 08:52.250
Nothing to worry about.

08:52.291 --> 08:55.917
- I don't get this!

08:52.291 --> 08:55.917
I'm indestructible!

08:55.959 --> 08:57.792
How's your freakish disease

08:55.959 --> 08:57.792
making me sick?!?

08:57.834 --> 08:59.875
- I guess I'm just really good

08:59.917 --> 09:03.000
at creating freakish diseases.

09:04.542 --> 09:06.417
- So you're positive

09:04.542 --> 09:06.417
we're not gonna die?

09:06.458 --> 09:08.583
- Of course!

09:08.625 --> 09:10.000
Well at least not until

09:10.041 --> 09:11.709
all of your fingers

09:10.041 --> 09:11.709
and thumbs turn green.

09:11.750 --> 09:13.750
- WHAT?!?

09:11.750 --> 09:13.750
- THEN WE DIE?!?

09:13.792 --> 09:15.417
- Look, you all just go inside

09:15.458 --> 09:18.542
so I can get back

09:15.458 --> 09:18.542
to working on the cure.

09:18.583 --> 09:21.250
- Wait but what if Henry's

09:18.583 --> 09:21.250
parents try to leave the house?

09:21.291 --> 09:22.792
- Don't worry...

09:22.834 --> 09:24.041
I brought Bork

09:22.834 --> 09:24.041
to guard the door.

09:24.083 --> 09:25.834
- Oh hey.

09:24.083 --> 09:25.834
- Heya Bork.

09:25.875 --> 09:28.625
- [ Bork grunts ]

09:28.667 --> 09:30.917
- Bork, come help

09:28.667 --> 09:30.917
me outta here!

09:35.583 --> 09:36.875
- AHHHH!!!

09:41.250 --> 09:42.417
Thanks.

09:42.458 --> 09:43.417
- [ Bork grunts ]

09:56.333 --> 09:57.500
- Hey...

09:57.542 --> 10:00.834
- Hi Henry.

09:57.542 --> 10:00.834
- Hello.

10:00.875 --> 10:02.750
- Oh my gosh,

10:00.875 --> 10:02.750
is Charlotte sick too?

10:02.792 --> 10:05.458
- Yeah.

10:02.792 --> 10:05.458
- So's my boss.

10:05.500 --> 10:07.500
- That's right but...

10:07.542 --> 10:09.417
But I'm not too sick

10:07.542 --> 10:09.417
to notice a pretty li--

10:09.458 --> 10:12.959
[ coughing ]

10:14.834 --> 10:16.667
I need my pills.

10:16.709 --> 10:19.917
Give me my pi--

10:16.709 --> 10:19.917
Awww, come on!

10:21.583 --> 10:23.375
- Ah! Look honey...

10:23.417 --> 10:25.458
their fingers

10:23.417 --> 10:25.458
are turning green too!

10:25.500 --> 10:26.959
- Yeah, well...

10:27.000 --> 10:29.417
That's why I'm takin'

10:27.000 --> 10:29.417
us all to the doctor.

10:29.458 --> 10:31.959
- You can't!

10:29.458 --> 10:31.959
- Uh, actually you can't...

10:32.000 --> 10:34.667
- Mom, Dad, Piper...

10:32.000 --> 10:34.667
this is uh...

10:34.709 --> 10:37.375
- My name is

10:34.709 --> 10:37.375
Doctor Schwarmalensen.

10:39.166 --> 10:43.000
- Yeah, that.

10:39.166 --> 10:43.000
He's from the uh...

10:43.041 --> 10:44.291
- The Swellview County

10:43.041 --> 10:44.291
Health Department.

10:44.333 --> 10:45.834
- That's right.

10:45.875 --> 10:49.417
I'm sorry but you must

10:45.875 --> 10:49.417
all be quarantined.

10:49.458 --> 10:52.458
- Quarantined?!?

10:49.458 --> 10:52.458
- Yes.

10:52.500 --> 10:54.291
You see, little girl...

10:54.333 --> 10:57.625
when people get upset tum-tums,

10:54.333 --> 10:57.625
sometimes they have--

10:57.667 --> 11:01.959
- Will you quit talking to me

10:57.667 --> 11:01.959
like I'm an idiot?

11:02.000 --> 11:04.083
- It just means that

11:02.000 --> 11:04.083
we have to stay here,

11:04.125 --> 11:06.750
in this house,

11:04.125 --> 11:06.750
until he says we're cured.

11:06.792 --> 11:08.792
- Uh, yes,

11:06.792 --> 11:08.792
that's right, uh...

11:08.834 --> 11:12.000
- Okay, sorry

11:08.834 --> 11:12.000
Doctor Schwankelsen,

11:12.041 --> 11:14.208
but I'm not going to the doctor,

11:14.250 --> 11:16.333
and I don't want to sit

11:14.250 --> 11:16.333
in this stupid house all day.

11:16.375 --> 11:18.834
- Piper...

11:16.375 --> 11:18.834
- I'm going to Glozella!

11:18.875 --> 11:21.125
- No! No no...

11:18.875 --> 11:21.125
- Please don't.

11:23.458 --> 11:26.041
- [ growls ]

11:30.291 --> 11:32.875
- I've decided to stay here.

11:32.917 --> 11:34.208
- [ growling ]

11:36.917 --> 11:38.709
- Okay, I don't mean

11:36.917 --> 11:38.709
any disrespect,

11:38.750 --> 11:41.583
but I just don't see why

11:38.750 --> 11:41.583
we can't go see our own doctor.

11:41.625 --> 11:43.834
- No!

11:43.875 --> 11:47.417
If you come into contact

11:43.875 --> 11:47.417
with the public,

11:47.458 --> 11:50.959
you could infect

11:47.458 --> 11:50.959
every person in Swellview.

11:51.000 --> 11:53.333
- Yeah mom, we're contagious,

11:53.375 --> 11:54.834
we can't risk

11:53.375 --> 11:54.834
infecting other people.

11:57.250 --> 11:59.333
- Hey...

11:59.375 --> 12:01.417
uh, where did that

11:59.375 --> 12:01.417
bratty little girl go?

12:03.709 --> 12:04.625
- Piper went out the back!

12:04.667 --> 12:06.333
- We gotta stop her!

12:06.375 --> 12:07.834
- Piper!

12:07.875 --> 12:09.625
- Hey! Quit it!

12:09.667 --> 12:12.458
Put me down you...

12:12.500 --> 12:14.125
you large man!

12:17.792 --> 12:19.875
- Yes...

12:19.917 --> 12:24.125
I think you will all

12:19.917 --> 12:24.125
find escape quite impossible.

12:25.500 --> 12:26.875
See you soon!

